1) Board can be of any size
2) Each player puts their counter on the board starting position
3) Take turns to roll the dice
4) Move your counter forward based on the spaces shown after rolling the dice
5) If the counter lands at the bottom of the ladder then the counter is moved to top of the ladder
6) If the counter lands at the head of the snake then the counter is moved down to the tail of the snake
7) Each player will get a fair chance to roll the dice
8) Game is continued till there are two players left
9) User has to reach the exact destinationi.e, when a user is located at 99th position and requires
   to go forawrd by 1 block for reaching destination. User needs to roll a `1` on the dice to reach
   and not more than `1`. 